{"tid":1067882,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多人會用牙線???","createTime":"2019-03-19T00:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T03:34:33.000Z","uid":132931,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"839019b65a2ddb288e9d908bfc435276cc329a04","tid":1067882,"uid":132931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T00:25:45.000Z","msg":"想知大家平時有無用開牙線的習慣???<br />\n話說岩岩試下用牙線啦,發覺用牙線都幾麻煩,一黎唔就位,2黎隻隻牙都要用.<br />\n之後用完條牙線臭到仆街.我諗D牙縫應該勁撚臭.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴絲係每日堅持用牙線??<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510ade5b836a1f81135d0d3b7221fc0ab73c211a","tid":1067882,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T00:30:18.000Z","msg":"用慣咗其實清潔曬所有牙只需30秒或更少<br />\n如果牙生得唔齊整會難啲同耐啲"},{"pid":"ddb7bd0aa4164ad2a1c43cfa0d3a0d50ccf3e466","tid":1067882,"uid":53592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T00:30:19.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"26ee5a8acdc7020c36392d925362d8d8289bce34","tid":1067882,"uid":56843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T00:33:45.000Z","msg":"我用完條牙線唔臭<br />\n不如你考慮用埋漱口水"},{"pid":"86804abac32c08fd74bd941de608efca66ab8dd9","tid":1067882,"uid":18566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T00:35:27.000Z","msg":"每晚都用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac67bb019dd9ede2cd00e0e5c2f120db7893f5d5","tid":1067882,"uid":745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T00:35:28.000Z","msg":"要用"},{"pid":"ef79da5be28b900f87f046408a4494a348a9125f","tid":1067882,"uid":140631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T00:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用咗好耐都唔識點刷上排入面堆牙"},{"pid":"281af081f56850adef21b28801050524b3b1777c","tid":1067882,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T01:30:39.000Z","msg":"用水牙線 